item.dc:creator: @jordan7 Jordan7
item.description:
@jordan7 wrote:

Yes, and also if you want it so when new players join they start a spawn point go to Player.Java
then search

// the first call to updateThisPlayerMovement() will craft the proper initialization packet

Under that you should see something like this (My X & Y location are for varrock castle)

teleportToX = 3212;//3212; teleportToY = 3467;//3467;

Change the coords to where you want them to start…
